title: Dreadstar and Company
description: My name is Oedi and I soar amidst the stars far from the planet of my birth. I guess this starship is the closest thing I've got to a home now, for I am a refugee and an outlaw. These days, the Empirical Galaxy is peppered with people like me. It's an easy club to join – all you have to do is be in the wrong place at the wrong time and…BINGO…you're a member. One finds that there are very few right places to be when a 200-year-old war rages about you.
